A vast landscape seen from above showing a terrain that gradually blends from deep red earth on one side through rich purple valleys in the middle to deep blue forests on the other side, rendered in Studio Ghibli style with soft watercolor textures and gentle rolling hills. The colors merge seamlessly into each other rather than forming harsh borders, with small clusters of warmly-lit villages scattered throughout all color zones, their tiny glowing windows suggesting communities existing peacefully across the gradient. Wispy clouds drift overhead casting soft shadows, and a winding river connects all regions, its water reflecting the surrounding hues. The perspective suggests unity within apparent division, the whole scene bathed in golden hour light that softens all boundaries.
